Roles &amp; Responsibilities

  Basic and Full Grooming of dogs and cats.
  Ensure safety of pets throughout the grooming process.
  Clean and maintenance of grooming area in the shop.
  Able to work in a team with colleagues.
  Washing and prepping the animals for grooming.
  Managing animal waste.

Requirements

  Require&nbsp;handling pets&nbsp;(dogs and cats) with care.
  Cannot be sensitive or allergic to washing chemical or pet fur.
  Willing to learn on the job.
